
----------------------------------------------------
Pre-requisites (One time setup)
----------------------------------------------------
1. Goto 'http://gradle.org/downloads' and download 'gradle-1.0-milestone-7-all.zip'

2. Unzip it to your system. Setup a GRADLE_HOME environment variable and add it to the PATH
   (i.e.: PATH=%PATH%;%GRADLE_HOME%\bin)
   Detail installation instruction can be found at http://gradle.org/docs/current/userguide/installation.html

3. Download the Gradle Artifactory plugin 
   http://wiki.jfrog.org/confluence/display/RTF/Gradle+Artifactory+Plugin
   copy the jar to your home path ~/.gradle/plugin

4. Create a gradle.properties in the ~/.gradle path with the following contents

   hwp_company="Highwire Press"
   artifactory_user=deployer
   artifactory_password={DESede}vux+bfjRSOCG6eLUqBPoUA==
   dev_user=devbuild
   dev_password={DESede}AKnZq9J6gwMitWC5BOrpbQ==


